            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華新(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1605-TW</a>)28日10:37股價上漲2.85元，報43.45元，漲幅7.02%，成交146,574張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華新(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1605-TW</a>)所屬產業為電器電纜，主要業務為電線電纜、鋼線鋼纜及特殊鋼之生產與銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌4.25%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.76%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-46,813 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-27,877 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-12,963 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-5,973 張</li> <li>融資增減：+431 張</li> <li>融券增減：+355 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
